<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>마이페이지</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mypage.css">
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>

<main class="mypage-container">
    <div class="mypage-header">
        <h2>마이페이지</h2>
        {{#myPage.loggedInUser}}
            <p>환영합니다, <strong>{{myPage.username}}</strong>님!</p>
        {{/myPage.loggedInUser}}
        {{^myPage.loggedInUser}}
            <p>로그인하시면 더 많은 혜택을 누리실 수 있습니다.</p>
        {{/myPage.loggedInUser}}
    </div>

    <div class="auth-links">
        {{#myPage.loggedInUser}}
            <p><a href="/logout">로그아웃</a></p>
        {{/myPage.loggedInUser}}
        {{^myPage.loggedInUser}}
            <p><a href="/login">로그인하기</a></p>
            <p><a href="/signup">회원가입하기</a></p>
        {{/myPage.loggedInUser}}
    </div>

    <ul class="mypage-menu">
        {{#myPage.menuList}}
            <li>
                <a href="{{link}}">
                    {{text}}
                    {{#isNew}}<span class="new-badge">신규</span>{{/isNew}}
                    <span class="arrow-icon">&gt;</span>
                </a>
            </li>
        {{/myPage.menuList}}
    </ul>
</main>
</body>
</html>